<div class="hero">
    <h1>🌍 CityList API</h1>
    <p>Comprehensive worldwide city database with geographic coordinates</p>
</div>

<div class="stats">
    <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number"><%= cityCount || '200K+' %></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Cities Worldwide</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">195+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Countries</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">API v1</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Latest Version</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">GeoNames</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Data Source</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>🚀 Quick Start</h2>
    <p>Get started with the CityList API in seconds:</p>
    
    <h3>Search Cities</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /api/v1/cities/search?q=london</code></pre>
    
    <h3>Get City by ID</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /api/v1/cities/2643743</code></pre>
    
    <h3>Get Cities by Country</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /api/v1/cities/country/US</code></pre>
    
    <h3>Find Nearest City</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /api/v1/cities/coordinates?longitude=-0.12574&latitude=51.50853</code></pre>
    
    <h3>Get Full Dataset</h3>
    <pre><code>GET /api/data</code></pre>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>📊 Features</h2>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>200,000+</strong> cities worldwide</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Geographic coordinates</strong> (latitude, longitude)</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Country codes</strong> (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2)</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Compatible</strong> with OpenWeatherMap API</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>RESTful API</strong> with JSON responses</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Rate limiting</strong> (1000 requests/hour)</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>CORS enabled</strong> for web applications</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Swagger documentation</strong> available</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">✅ <strong>Geolocation support</strong> for finding nearest cities</li>
    </ul>
</div>

